Query:
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW SALES.V_Odoo_Sales
AS 
SELECT * FROM SALES.ODOO_SALES;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW CLIENT.V_Odoo_Customers
AS
SELECT * FROM CLIENT.ODOO_CUSTOMERS;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW LOGISTICS.V_Odoo_Inventory
AS
SELECT * FROM LOGISTICS.ODOO_INVENTORY;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW SALES.V_ODOO_SALES_MERGED
AS 
SELECT OS.ID, OS.PRODUCT_NAME,
OS.PRODUCT_CATEGORY, OS.PRODUCT_CODE, OS.PRICE, OS.PRICE_LIST, 
OS.QUANTITY AS QUANTITY_SOLD, OS.COUNTRY, OS.DUKA_NAME, OS.SHOP_KEEPER,
OC.NAME AS CLIENT_NAME, OC.PHONE_NUMBER AS CLIENT_PHONENUMBER,  OS.CREATED_AT, OS.CREATED_BY
FROM SALES.ODOO_SALES OS
JOIN CLIENT.ODOO_CUSTOMERS OC ON OC.USER_ID = OS.CUSTOMER_ID

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW CLIENT.V_KOBO_SEASONAL_CLIENTS_ENROLLMENTS
AS SELECT 
	ID,
	KOBO_ID,
	SUBMISSION_ID,
	NURSERY,
	DUKA,
	USERNAME,
	FARMER_NAME,
	FARMER_ID,
	FARMER_PHONE_NUMBER,
	TUPANDE_FARMER,
	SITE,
	OTHER_SITE,
	SECTOR,
	REGION,
	COUNTRY,
	DISTRICT,
	SEASON,
	YEAR,
	START_TIME,
	END_TIME,
	SUBMISSION_TIME,
	SUBMITTED_BY,
	IS_DELETED,
	SOURCE,
	DB_CREATED_AT,
	DB_UPDATED_AT
FROM CLIENT.KOBO_SEASONAL_CLIENTS_ENROLLMENTS;
